tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE time_series_data(
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    value FLOAT,
    
    PRIMARY KEY (timestamp)
)

CREATE TABLE TimeSeriesData (
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    value FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE AggregatedData (
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    avg_value FLOAT,
    sum_value FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE AnalyzedData (
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    moving_avg FLOAT,
    row_number INT,
    running_total FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE lag_lead_data (
    timestamp TIMESTAMPTZ,
    device_id INT,
    value FLOAT,
    lag_value FLOAT,
    lead_value FLOAT
);
